metadata.name: Honest Santa #1
metadata.description:
Honest Santa #1 - 2022 was a bad year for most crypto fans specially with long and bloody bear market.
Guess what?? Our cute Honest Santa is here specially for you to change things up. Because if you've minted your own Honest Santa, it means you're here in the market standing strong as a diamond hand and a true believer in crypto future. So, Santa is here to bring you hope, joy and happiness.
Merry Christmas
